        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/8bbacc5c12ebacaa855340096bce5027?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
                "account_id": 1015060,
                "user_type": "registered",
                "user_id": 1026805,
                "link": "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1026805/sri-harsha-chilakapati",
                "reputation": 12021,
                "display_name": "Sri Harsha Chilakapati",
                "accept_rate": 86
            },
            "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
            "score": 1,
            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1377659384,
            "creation_date": 1377659384,
            "body": "<p>Try running in a new Thread.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>new Thread(new Runnable()\n{\n    public void run()\n    {\n        Thread.sleep(45000);\n        System.out.println(\"My message\");\n    }\n})\n.run();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>This should work.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 18478766,
            "question_id": 18478677
        },
        {
