            "creation_date": 1377658924,
            "body": "<p>Just tell the thread to sleep for 45 seconds, there is a tutorial here:<\/p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/essential/concurrency/sleep.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/essential/concurrency/sleep.html<\/a><\/p>\n",
