            "last_activity_date": 1377659324,
            "creation_date": 1377659324,
            "body": "<p>Tell the main thread to sleep might not be ideal as it will cause your program to basically stop. Use a another thread(need to do a little multi-threading) for timing your output and do a check if the message should be printed after the 45s.<\/p>\n",
